      "content": "it just feels like there's nothing left to let go of. the \"fighting\" i'm doing is just trying to keep this shell moving through the day. when you say it might be more compassionate to stop fighting... does that mean just giving up? like, finally letting the silence happen instead of trying to fill it?",
